channel.title: Loretto/Altoona/Johnstown Pennsylvania Go Baby Go at SFU
channel.description: Hello we are just getting a Go Baby Go Chapter started in Loretto Pennsylvania at Saint Francis University. Loretto is 80 miles to the east of Pittsburgh, 25 miles North of Johnstown and 18 miles West of Altoona. Please contact Dr. Heather Mack at hmack@francis.edu for questions and assistance! We did our first test build 2-8-19 and successfully completed a Lil Lightening McQueen Build. We will be doing our first big build March 16, 2019.
